{"tid":1385394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"長文慎入 舊登巴打對香城ONLINE 2.0 728改版更新睇法","createTime":"2019-07-30T05:23:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-31T08:01:06.000Z","uid":21108,"like":23,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"5ca51485dec8c84e42fcd71395b5abe67338d60e","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:23:18.000Z","msg":"首先 本人為隔離登巴打 <br />\n借Acc開post 唔識規矩多多包容<br />\n每次都有Online希望打上100層紅玉宮<br />\n但對於最近改版去到樽頸 有d建議<br />\n<br />\n對於和理非 + 半勇武(敢企前線本人係尊重既)<br />\n<br />\n1. 關於有人掉野 <br />\n<br />\n不要說 : 咪撚掉啦<br />\n試著說 : 要幾個同時掉 掉完就閃<br />\n<br />\n打仗都係一排火鎗射出去,成組遠攻掉先有威脅<br />\n俾人射到仆街,仲打唔還手係咪撞襯個頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 關於玩火  <br />\n<br />\n請不要阻止 , 民意儲氣已經升級 鑑於敵人已經開鎗恆常化 催淚放題變日常<br />\n連中立NPC都俾捕 理由係協助暴動 燒個火又算D乜?<br />\n<br />\n如果你連火都唔敢用 就唔好企前線去轉職啦  淆底行返後少少  <span style=\"color: red;\">用火緊記由底燒起</span><br />\n<br />\n3. 如果閣下FULL GEAR但又唔敢進攻 唔緊要<br />\n勇武需要你在場精神支持 其他事你唔敢 唔好阻人做 香城ONLINE各有各做<br />\n<br />\n當班敵人尤其恐龍衝上黎 你可以預備手上工具 掉出去嚇停敵人保護我方撤退<br />\n只要你地中排願意 唔係出黎打卡 到此一遊 幫到撒退已經救到好多我方<br />\n<br />\n4. 前線排位<br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/30/TOYn16.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2FTOYn16.jpeg&h=204a2669&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n前線要維持防線但唔需要好密 有咩事後面有兩個身位轉身跑<br />\n鑑於728太多人踩人同<span style=\"color: red;\">前排掉裝備問題 導致前線勇武走唔切俾捕</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">甚至令到救煙隊 FA隊都撞埋一堆</span> 又唔係要反推 咁多人咁密做乜  呢點真係要檢討  <br />\n有人會問 另外多出黎既人手會去左邊 我地最大優勢係人數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 下文會講<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋唔該各位請帶走自己既GEAR!!!! 如果連俾敵人逗你都驚 咁你出黎做乜撚野?<br />\n俾狗逗到D裝備又可以點 沒收左 唔係放人就要去臭格 <br />\n<br />\n728 有49位GAMEOVER 去左臭格啦!!! 你發夢Online乜柒都無做去坐返48小時出黎有咩問題<br />\n你知唔知而家D裝備越黎越少啦 物資車唔係課金就有 好撚危險 有D前線連飯都無得食呀!!!</span><br />\n<br />\n另外講前線有班初試勇武果班有隔離登巴打講左 呢樣慳返<br />\n<a href=\"https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7091580/page/1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewweb.hkgolden.com%2Fthread%2F7091580%2Fpage%2F1&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=50d2c363\" target=\"_blank\">https://newweb.hkgolden.com/thread/7091580/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n唔該人人自危 幫手保存資源!!!  你地可以做既盡做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/07/30/pGbTPC.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F07%2F30%2FpGbTPC.jpeg&h=85ee6a81&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n關於勇武派建議<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">可以將開波時間壓縮 唔使磨到最後 防線未齊就要主動出擊 以快打慢<br />\n<br />\n要訂下目標 想做D咩就要全力衝 如發現未能成功就要退</span><br />\n<br />\n而講緊退係 轉場也好 收隊也好 要係安全時間離開 <br />\n敵人由發現再進攻太概8分鐘內仍然安全 但夜間會更短 SOURCE FORM INTERNET<br />\n最後由和理非自行散場 解散 <span style=\"color: red;\">(和理非人數太多 敵人係唔會捉得晒 但勇武好易成TARGET)</span><br />\n<br />\n其次 如果防線已經形成 我地有咁多人手係後面可以做D咩呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n好攰要休息齋坐???  NO~ 要去令敵手感到無所適從 疲於奔命<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">所以要減少前線負擔 最好狀態既數小時解決</span><br />\n同樣 最後由和理非自行散場 解散<br />\n<br />\n可即場組隊 自行解任務 搵緊急任務做 敵人識搵落單我地都識 敵人包圍我地都識 <br />\n游擊更加係我地既優勢  如見到警車要俾禮貌問候時常識吧? <br />\n<br />\n最後送上香城ONLINE 2.0 之 香港地。戰爭<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AH5sGUWugd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DAH5sGUWugd4&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e0dadaa0\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AH5sGUWugd4</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBh7Dzi97L0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DqBh7Dzi97L0&d=BNsYvnDu2JTLJ%2Bl7stKmI%2Fo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=20f3eebf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=qBh7Dzi97L0</a>"},{"pid":"d725b43dceda1cf736f05ed1f306d1971b2a382d","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"3539d2b892d8db7f36526214f12a3a61516c9866","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:24:36.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"0796cf2e9c4b3a97af8498052ff07e6964c510b8","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce6b3b18eaad99cf3cd2d48dace2e2901ac34f7f","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"27d085c4710701b7ded20221f7588c7b2e46f069","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e061e72949c18e9a80796203c284983aee5e23e5","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:26:54.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"47a57903811f5082c205625ed2ea884298fb6808","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f8cb5654c32eff337047aee701a3e0e45bd42e82","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4c107d44aeb97cd350ac9688be8978c3f3069432","tid":1385394,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6ed8b002f156fd5259776f65380938aacbdc963c","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:07.000Z","msg":"十連~"},{"pid":"1865964ffcf05717ccd1fdaa0a1aece7a0ff9faf","tid":1385394,"uid":21108,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c107d44aeb97cd350ac9688be8978c3f3069432","tid":1385394,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:28:59.000Z","msg":"推"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T05:29:33.000Z","msg":"多謝幫推"},{"pid":"9e068f1f0fdb999e4b440b1b707451722c934c8c","tid":1385394,"uid":260035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"